    <para>

</para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">Max delay</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> It defines the largest value the time delay input can have.The value cannot be negative.</para>
        <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">initial input</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> The output generated by the block until the simulation time first exceeds the time delay input.</para>
        <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">Buffer size</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> The number of points the block can store.</para>
        <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </refsection>
